      <title>肯尼亚总统迫于压力放弃 23 亿美元税收计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/kenya-president-bends-to-pressure-scraps-2-3-billion-tax-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚总统威廉·鲁托表示，他将撤回一项有争议的税收法案，此前针对该法案征收 23 亿美元新税的计划引发的抗议活动导致至少 23 人死亡，迫使公众施加压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/kenya-president-bends-to-pressure-scraps-2-3-billion-tax-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 13:56:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通用磨坊股价因购物者减少而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-26/general-mills-shares-drop-as-shoppers-pull-back-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[通用磨坊预计本财年的有机销售额将在持平和增长 1% 之间，低于分析师平均预期的 1.18%。该公司预计本财年的销量趋势将逐渐改善，但预计美元增长将低于长期增长预测。西蒙妮·福克斯曼报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-26/general-mills-shares-drop-as-shoppers-pull-back-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 13:54:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰为何需要与债券持有人达成新协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/ukraine-economy-why-kyiv-needs-a-new-deal-with-its-bondholders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[距离乌克兰 200 亿美元债券的两年延期还款期结束仅剩几周时间，乌克兰必须恢复向私人债权人支付利息。债务重组谈判迄今未能达成协议，双方在债券持有人应牺牲多少投资的问题上争执不休。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/ukraine-economy-why-kyiv-needs-a-new-deal-with-its-bondholders</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 13:50:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本财长菅田表示高度关注日元走势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/japan-s-kanda-says-watching-yen-with-high-level-of-urgency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本货币政策主管表示，政府正高度关注日元汇率走势，并将近期汇率走势描述为快速、一边倒，并发出升级警告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/japan-s-kanda-says-watching-yen-with-high-level-of-urgency</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 13:23:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乔丹离职后，瑞士央行选择内部人士施莱格尔领导瑞士央行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/snb-chief-will-be-schlegel-as-switzerland-opts-for-continuity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在瑞士政府选择不任命外部人士来打破现状后，瑞士国家银行副行长马丁·施莱格尔 (Martin Schlegel) 成功晋升为该银行的最高职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/snb-chief-will-be-schlegel-as-switzerland-opts-for-continuity</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元跌至 1986 年以来最低水平，增加了干预风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/yen-weakens-beyond-key-160-level-raising-risk-of-intervention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元跌至1986年以来的最低水平，引发人们猜测当局可能很快被迫再次支持日元，以阻止发达国家最严重的抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/yen-weakens-beyond-key-160-level-raising-risk-of-intervention</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 09:39:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长雷恩认为 2024 年再降息两次是合理的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/ecb-s-rehn-sees-bets-for-two-more-cuts-in-2024-as-reasonable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会成员奥利·雷恩表示，投资者对欧洲央行今年将再放松两次货币政策——到 2025 年将借贷成本降至 2.25% 的预期是合理的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/ecb-s-rehn-sees-bets-for-two-more-cuts-in-2024-as-reasonable</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 04:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
